{
    "name": "w06_c10_03.ks",
    "lines": [
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 11
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "レジャーシートを片付けて、荷物を海の家へ預けたあと、\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 12
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "俺と智花はのんびりと海で遊んだ。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 13
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 16
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "時間を追うにつれて、夏の終わりの海は少し肌寒くなり、\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 17
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "海水浴客が減っていった。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 18
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 26
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "そして……あっという間に、一日が終わろうとしていた。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 27
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031408"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 37
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「んっ……風が強くなってきたわね……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 38
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 41
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "智花は、風に踊る髪の毛を押さえながら、沖の方へ視線を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 42
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "向けた。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 43
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 46
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "日の高いうちはずっと日陰にいたためか、智花の肌は朝と\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 47
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "変わらずにまっ白なままだった。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 48
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 51
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "夕日に照らされたその白い身体は、きらきらと輝いていて、\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 52
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "さながら１枚の絵画のようだった。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 53
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031409"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 58
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「夕日が沈んでいくわね……水平線がきらきらして、\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 59
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　すごく綺麗だわ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 60
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 63
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「そ、そうだな」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 64
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 69
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "まるで俺の心情を読んだかのような言葉にどきりとする。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 70
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031410"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 75
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「なんだか不思議ね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 76
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 79
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "どちらともなく歩調がゆっくりとしたものになり、やがて\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 80
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "止まった。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 81
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 84
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「……なにがだ？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 85
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031411"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 90
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「この間まで、姉弟がばらばらになってしまいそうな\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 91
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　大問題があったのに、今はすっかり日常が戻って\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 92
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　きているんだもの」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 93
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 96
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「そうだな……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 97
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 102
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "父さんと母さんは、喧嘩をする前と同じように二人で店を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 103
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "開けている。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 104
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 107
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "いずみ姉さんは相変わらず生徒会活動で忙しそうにして\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 108
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "いるし、みこと姉ちゃんは運動部の助っ人をやめて店を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 109
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "手伝ったりつまみ食いをしたりと家に入り浸っている。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 110
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 113
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "弥恵は厨房を手伝ったり、智花と一緒に家事をしたり\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 114
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "しているし、絵麻は弥恵のあとや俺のあとに\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 115
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "くっついて歩いている。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 116
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 119
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "全部が元通りになったのだ。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 120
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 123
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「でも……」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 124
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031412"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 129
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ん……なに？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 130
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 133
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "俺の呟きを聞きとがめて、智花は首を傾げた。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 134
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 137
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「変わったこともたくさんあるよ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 138
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031413"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 144
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「変わったこと？」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 145
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031414"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 151
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「そういえば、和哉はパティシエの修業を始めたものね」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 152
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 155
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「ああ、それもあるな」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 156
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 159
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "父さんと母さんは、どうやら本気で将来俺に店を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 160
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "持たせようと思っているらしい。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 161
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 164
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "普通であれば子どもの意志を無視するのかと抗議する\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 165
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "ところなのだろうが、俺自身もパティシエの道に興味を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 166
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "持ってしまっているのだからタチが悪い。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 167
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031415"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 172
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「将来有望だって、母さんたちが言ってたわよ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 173
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 176
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「本当か？　俺は怒られてばっかりだけどな」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 177
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 180
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "指導に熱が入りすぎて、深夜遅くまで厨房に居残り\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 181
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "させられることも少なくない。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 182
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031416"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 188
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「いいじゃない。目標があるっていうのは素敵なことだと\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 189
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "　思うわ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 190
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "和哉"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 193
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「カブに入ってる智花に言われると、説得力があるな」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 194
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 197
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "俺のお嫁さんになる——その夢のために、花嫁修業を\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 198
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "ずっと続けていてくれたのだから。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 199
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031417"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 205
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "「も、もう……あんまりにやにやしないで、怒るわよ」\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 206
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "心の声"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 209
        },
        {
            "line": {
                "text": "恥ずかしそうに口を尖らせる智花が可愛らしくて仕方ない。\r\n"
            },
            "annotation": {},
            "shouldShift": false,
            "shift": 0,
            "textNumber": 210
        },
        {
            "line": {},
            "annotation": {
                "type": "Talk",
                "values": [
                    {
                        "name": "智花"
                    },
                    {
                        "voice": "TM031418"
                    }
                ]
            },
